<plot>This Columbia "Thrills of Music" series short is not the same as the Paramount 1943 short carrying the same title. Ina Ray is again leading her all-male orchestra, with the beginning number a Hutton standard, "Angry", that was also featured in the Paramount short. That is followed by "Three Little Bears" and a rhumba number.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?606201</url></doc>
